Didier Flamand https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Didier_Flamand 0 Didier Flamand (born 12 March 1947) is a French actor and theatre director. He has appeared in more than 150 films and television shows since 1973. He starred in Raúl Ruiz's 1978 film The Suspended Vocation.
